Skulk - utility skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Swashbucklers of the more roguish sort often have reasons
for wanting to leave--or enter--a room unnoticed.  This
ability allows them to do just that.  If you wish to move
silently further than one room, you must use skulk each
time.

GL:  1
SP: 10
command:  skulk <direction>
duration: instant
